<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - SoleScape Footwear</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="container">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="./about.hbs">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#products">Products</a></li>
                <li><a href="#team">Team</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>SoleScape Footwear</h1>
            <p>Walk in comfort, style with confidence</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <main class="container">
        <section id="about">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p class="mission">Our mission is to provide high-quality, comfortable footwear that empowers individuals to
                pursue their passions with confidence and style.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="history" class="history">
            <div class="history-text">
                <h2>Our History</h2>
                <p>Founded in 2005, SoleScape began as a small workshop dedicated to crafting bespoke shoes for
                    discerning customers. Over the years, we've grown into a global brand, but our commitment to quality
                    and innovation remains unchanged.</p>
                <p>From our humble beginnings to our current status as a leader in footwear technology, we've always put
                    our customers' comfort and satisfaction first.</p>
            </div>
            <img src="/images/hero-banner.png" alt="SoleScape workshop">
        </section>

        <section id="products">
            <h2>Our Products</h2>
            <div class="products">
                <div class="product">
                    <img src="/images/cta-1.jpg" alt="Running Shoes">
                    <h3>Running Shoes</h3>
                    <p>Engineered for performance</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product">
                    <img src="/images/cta-2.jpg" alt="Casual Sneakers">
                    <h3>Casual Sneakers</h3>
                    <p>Comfort meets style</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product">
                    <img src="/images/collection-1.jpg" alt="Formal Shoes">
                    <h3>Formal Shoes</h3>
                    <p>Elegance in every step</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="team">
            <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
            <div class="team">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="/api/placeholder/150/150" alt="Jane Doe">
                    <h3>Jane Doe</h3>
                    <p>Founder & CEO</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="/api/placeholder/150/150" alt="John Smith">
                    <h3>John Smith</h3>
                    <p>Head of Design</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="/api/placeholder/150/150" alt="Emily Brown">
                    <h3>Emily Brown</h3>
                    <p>Chief Innovation Officer</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 SoleScape Footwear. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/about.js"></script>
